# MindfulNest — Architecture (LD-280 + master spec)

## Narrative / playback (LD-280)

- Every module is **one atomic MP4** played by **one `expo-video` instance**.
- Route: `/module/[moduleId]` only. **No** separate intro / phase_a / phase_b / resolution / win / decoration **screens**.
- Banned files (CI enforced): `app/intro.tsx`, `app/phase_a.tsx`, `app/phase_b.tsx`, `app/resolution.tsx`, `app/win.tsx`, `app/decoration.tsx`.
- **No** `expo-audio` in the module playback path. **No** cue-timed RN overlays over video.

## Map / home (master spec §3.2)

- **Shipping UX:** scrollable Everdale WebP map; child **taps creature sprites** to start a module — not a generic "Start module" button.
- Current `app/index.tsx` is a **Stage 1 dev scaffold** (placeholder text). Do not treat scaffold controls as kid-facing UI.
- Scaffold/dev controls must be **`__DEV__` only** — never visible in production/preview builds.

## Sentry (LD-801)

- Import `@sentry/react-native` **only** in `src/services/sentryService.ts`.
- All other files use the wrapper.

## Firebase auth imports

- Screens import from `src/services/auth.ts`, not `firebase/auth` directly.
